{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/cli-boxen","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"5b5c09f8-b3be-5264-8b5e-b6fb1c781db1","html":"<p>This is a series of libraries and utilities for building Command-line-interfaces aka CLI using Node.js and ecosystem around it. Similar utilities/helpers may be available for other languages but, these series is focused on JavaScript and its friends.</p>\n<p>You can check all articles under <a href=\"/category/cli-build-tool/\"><code class=\"language-text\">CLI Build Tool</code></a> tag.</p>\n<h2 id=\"boxen\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#boxen\" aria-label=\"boxen permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/boxen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">boxen</a></h2>\n<p>If you are building a CLI and need to present some good output wrapped in box! Yes, square box, ‘boxen’ is the tool for you. Just like you had seen boxes around output of <code class=\"language-text\">update-notifier</code>. It makes the CLI app more appealing.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/7a8f9/updatenotifier.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.83333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/8ac56/updatenotifier.webp 240w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/d3be9/updatenotifier.webp 480w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/e46b2/updatenotifier.webp 960w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/f992d/updatenotifier.webp 1440w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/882b9/updatenotifier.webp 1920w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/f98c2/updatenotifier.webp 2988w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/8ff5a/updatenotifier.png 240w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/e85cb/updatenotifier.png 480w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/d9199/updatenotifier.png 960w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/07a9c/updatenotifier.png 1440w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/29114/updatenotifier.png 1920w,\n/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/7a8f9/updatenotifier.png 2988w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/a408d387490a426343fe94359bea9c1c/d9199/updatenotifier.png\"\n          alt=\"Screenshot\"\n          title=\"Screenshot\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>It can present your application output in boxes with various styles like ‘double dashed’, ‘rounded corners’ along with some ‘margin’ and ‘padding’ options.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/ad3bb/boxen.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 28.333333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAIAAABM9SnKAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAdklEQVQY05WQ7QqAIAxFe5vUbBamrg/LiN7/lZoJUUFFcNif3QN3y5iwZ3jhnrgliexiShTQMsrFqGMSc0kzIsqWeJPTWtVem1mboMGjChYmA+Ox/ZQHhwv2a1P6oVrIdyrwT3mv3fECWbpwr52ItaF7k/8+bAM+lkIfbx1OFAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/8ac56/boxen.webp 240w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/d3be9/boxen.webp 480w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/e46b2/boxen.webp 960w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/f992d/boxen.webp 1440w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/882b9/boxen.webp 1920w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/44883/boxen.webp 2785w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/8ff5a/boxen.png 240w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/e85cb/boxen.png 480w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/d9199/boxen.png 960w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/07a9c/boxen.png 1440w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/29114/boxen.png 1920w,\n/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/ad3bb/boxen.png 2785w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/7f37ce2c33cdfd8312339aa0eebc892e/d9199/boxen.png\"\n          alt=\"Screenshot\"\n          title=\"Screenshot\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Boxen has a very easy to follow, simple to use API. Here is a code example:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> boxen <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'boxen'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">boxen</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'unicorn'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/*\n┌─────────────┐\n│             │\n│   unicorn   │\n│             │\n└─────────────┘\n*/</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">boxen</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'unicorn'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> margin<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> borderStyle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'double'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/*\n\n   ╔═════════════╗\n   ║             ║\n   ║   unicorn   ║\n   ║             ║\n   ╚═════════════╝\n\n*/</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>You can check out official <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/boxen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">repo</a> for all usage details.</p>\n<p>Github Repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/boxen\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">boxen</a></p>\n<hr>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/cli-boxen","tagSlugs":["/tag/cli/","/tag/tools/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-06-26T18:05:00.738Z","description":"Node.js CLI App helper to create boxes in the Terminal","tags":["CLI","Tools"],"title":"Tool of the Trade for CLI Apps - `Boxen` 🔲","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/cli-boxen"}}}